    <h2>What we do for nugget ice machines, and what we don't.</h2>

    <p><strong>We service:</strong> Scotsman Brilliance (N0422, N0622, N0922 plus variants), Hoshizaki FS Sliver Nugget (FS-1000MWH), Manitowoc R-Series (RNS-0385A, RNS-0820A, RFS variants), Follett medical-grade nugget, all sizes (under-counter through large modular), air-cooled and water-cooled and remote-condensed configurations, all refrigerants (R-22 legacy, R-134a, R-404A, R-290 with R-290 cert), auger drive systems including the extrusion mechanism, drive shaft seals.</p>

    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> new nugget machine installation (specialty installer trade); Sonic-branded retail dispensers (specialty chain franchise equipment); ice bin standalone replacement.</p>
