    <h2>What separates our nugget service from general ice machine repair.</h2>

    <ul class="reasons-list">
      <li><strong>Extrusion mechanism expertise.</strong> Nugget-specific component (NOT on flake or cube). Specific service knowledge required to distinguish extrusion wear (slush output) from upstream auger or refrigerant failure.</li>
